,bob@example.com,Bob,Smith,
Deploy to Railway
Push to GitHub
Create a new Railway project → connect repo
Add a Redis plugin — REDIS_URL is injected automatically
Set HUNTER_API_KEY, CLEARBIT_API_KEY, APOLLO_API_KEY in Variables
